        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 6. — A, distal width (DW) plotted against maximum length (ML) of femur in Rhinocerotinae indet. from the Ivand locality and some other Rhinocerotidae Owen, 1845 from Eurasia (Akkaşdaşi data from Antoine & Saraç [2005]; Linxia data from Deng [2002]); B, ulna proximal width (PW) plotted against its width at process olecrani (POW) in Deinotherium giganteum Kaup, 1829 from Ivand locality and several other specimens from Europe (Unterzolling data from Huttunen & Göhlich 2002)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4597147/files/figure.png" .

